headline: How Recent Developments Are Rewriting the Story for Cracker Barrel
summary: Cracker Barrel Old Country Store’s fair value estimate has been trimmed slightly, from $47 to $46.38 per share. Analysts have also nudged the discount rate upward to reflect increased perceived risk. These modest revisions come on the heels of the company’s latest earnings report and updated guidance, which sparked new debate around the brand’s turnaround prospects.
